Source: MAF Agricultural Glossary
Author:
Vol / Page: 5
Edition:
Quote: Draft off: Removing certain animals from a group. This can be done by driving the animals out of a group (cut off or drift off) or driving them up a race and removing them through a special gate (drafting gate).
